34
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:25,120
[SPEAKER_01] Bio bi poput, oh, da, sigurno.

35
00:02:25,199 --> 00:02:26,080
[SPEAKER_01] A vi ste poput, što je to?

36
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:27,599
[SPEAKER_01] Da, Christian Seelig, zaista?

37
00:02:27,759 --> 00:02:27,840
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

38
00:02:28,879 --> 00:02:28,960
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

39
00:02:29,199 --> 00:02:29,280
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

40
00:02:29,599 --> 00:02:30,479
