60
00:05:05,439 --> 00:05:09,040
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, on je samo rekao: Evo, ne moraš miješati, samo mi daj cijelu godinu.

61
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:10,240
[SPEAKER_00] A ja sam rekao: Done.

62
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:11,600
[SPEAKER_00] Trebao sam pregovarati, čovječe.

63
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:16,639
