81
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:13,519
[SPEAKER_00] I to je puno posla, Bože Bože.

82
00:07:13,759 --> 00:07:15,519
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da je vrijednost ponude 2.

83
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:16,800
[SPEAKER_01] izbačena.

84
00:07:16,959 --> 00:07:17,759
[SPEAKER_01] To je puno posla.

85
00:07:17,839 --> 00:07:20,800
