98
00:08:46,559 --> 00:08:47,840
[SPEAKER_01] To je potpuno drugačiji posao.

99
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,440
[SPEAKER_01] Ne radim na razvoju iOS-a.

100
00:08:50,000 --> 00:09:00,960
